{"tid":1866590,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（整合）微博 #我要言论自由#","createTime":"2020-02-06T20:07:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T05:31:15.000Z","uid":312147,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f13254e7495d7b746caa7103288e47998e77d7b5","tid":1866590,"uid":312147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T20:07:02.000Z","msg":"截至凌晨3:46<br />\n有超過108萬瀏覽、6千條評論<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qLiXgTx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqLiXgTx.png&h=6cc2290b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n12點開始有兩個評論，幾十個瀏覽<br />\n高峰期係凌晨2-3點<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/edrBxsP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FedrBxsP.png&h=d1d49bb5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VV8DLNQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVV8DLNQ.png&h=216b3235&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fQgND7R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfQgND7R.png&h=9ad6dfb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇下有咩熱門評論<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3kH1JAn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3kH1JAn.png&h=4c35df22&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RqXdzG2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRqXdzG2.png&h=cf2ef020&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hmb2s13.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHmb2s13.png&h=880551ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n基本上都係講第35條乜乜自由<br />\n<br />\n最熱門個評論下面有咩留言？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VH9jvfS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVH9jvfS.png&h=241845d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼續睇埋落去<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/635OoB2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F635OoB2.png&h=1fdebe64&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C3SdzJH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC3SdzJH.png&h=540fc7db&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/psMaBW3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpsMaBW3.png&h=7dda4f93&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4oRBxvp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4oRBxvp.png&h=27c9f21c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZM6FeJK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZM6FeJK.png&h=ead2844b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好太興奮 只係好小規模嘅覺醒<br />\n但願種子已埋下 革命悄悄開始<br />\n<br />\nbtw, RIP 李醫生<br />\n唔會當你係手足<br />\n不過你係真&middot;中國人"},{"pid":"7a50f0ad09aaae8be8e7342737b5547a6963e227","tid":1866590,"uid":130035,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T20:19:02.000Z","msg":"見撚到啲廢青言論真係扯曬火<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1313935bec017e02502fcbaeeb3c8226eb144994","tid":1866590,"uid":321803,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T20:21:57.000Z","msg":"5年前我地都接受唔到暴力<br />\n願中共早日被推翻<br />\n<br />\n天滅中共"},{"pid":"6388802d46ff0cac85573e9fd1133695fe6fa243","tid":1866590,"uid":230039,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T20:23:55.000Z","msg":"天滅中共<br />\n<br />\n芝麻人冇一個係蘑菇的"},{"pid":"0c17d93ce880b4149b68269ba032d97366955f40","tid":1866590,"uid":35364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T20:25:55.000Z","msg":"對香港示威評價好兩極，<br />\n支持香港人數明顯係較少。<br />\n大多數都只係微博講兩句，<br />\n我覺得今次會不了了之。"},{"pid":"cfee200be82f96c59d40b3330779fbcec04f467e","tid":1866590,"uid":31389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T20:27:00.000Z","msg":"啱呀<br />\n微博叫兩聲就有言論自由架喇<br />\n叫大聲啲比官老爺聽啦"},{"pid":"044d08ad611e472e9291f281af2da4ab3ec3cd91","tid":1866590,"uid":312147,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0c17d93ce8